						               													<description>Familiy Frakass is a Beat them up board game.&amp;#10;It&amp;rsquo;s a 1 to 3 players cooperative boardgame based on the main characteristic than Beat them up game: Hit, Strike, Weapons, Combo, Henchmen, Boss...&amp;#10;The objective is quite simple, clean the board of each scene of the stage to reach the Boss. Beat it and continue on the next stage.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player will have a character with their own  specificities.&amp;#10;Then the game will switch between 2 phases: The Player turn and the Game turn.&amp;#10;During the Player turn, the player will use up to 3 action points to make his character moves, strikes or one of the 10 actions available for him.&amp;#10;The only main rules to follow there is: &amp;ldquo;A player cannot do the same action twice in the row during his turn.&amp;rdquo; (Means, you can Move, Strike and Move, but you cannot Move, Move, and Strike.)&amp;#10;Then when players finish their turn, the Game turn will start and the game will move by itself following 5 main actions. Those actions are also link to the action&amp;#10;Then it will be to the player turn again.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Regarding the Strike part, player will use colors cards common to all players. Each Heroes character have his own combos. A combo is a specific combination of colors. Means you will have to choose between use your cards of save it to prepare the combo.&amp;#10;You can now add Weapons, Group combo, Character posture and lots of mechanism for more fun and strike! (^_^)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If I try to explains this game by &amp;ldquo;mechanism&amp;rdquo;, I would say that an Action evolutive Puzzle, because the situation will change at every Game turn depending of the action done by player(s).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
